			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p79083">External Battery Charger Accessory</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=79083&amp;sid=9144880458ee87a9ea9f6797a9f88b61#p79083"><img src="./styles/robotreviews/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=16183&amp;sid=9144880458ee87a9ea9f6797a9f88b61">deepcscuba</a></strong> &raquo; June 1st, 2010, 12:36 am </p>

			

			<div class="content">Is there an external battery charger accessory available?  I couldn't find one on the <a href="http://www.robotreviews.com/cgi-bin/jump/jump.cgi?67" class="th23autolinks postlink" onclick="this.target='_blank';" rel="nofollow">iRobot</a> site, and <a href="http://www.robotreviews.com/cgi-bin/jump/jump.cgi?26" class="th23autolinks postlink" onclick="this.target='_blank';" rel="nofollow">Amazon</a> listed one, but looks like no stock for quite some time based on the reviews.  I'd like to run my 400 series as often as possible, and having an extra battery charging while the unit is running would be helpful.</div>

			

		</div>

		
